"692","Additional Information About Minimum Required Investment"
"693","Shareholders can open a fund account with as little as $500 and"
"694","make subsequent investments in any amount. The minimum"
"695","investment is waived if you make regular investments weekly,"
"696","semi-monthly, or monthly through automatic deductions through"
"697","your bank checking or savings account. Currently, Putnam is"
"698","waiving the minimum, but reserves the right to reject initial"
"699","investments under the minimum."
